{"tid":511041,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"打吡戰統計 美斯全場有8成時間在步行","createTime":"2017-12-27T05:42:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T07:02:37.000Z","uid":55981,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"47c7ee7d309d7a2d680407be01ed558519059793","tid":511041,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:42:11.000Z","msg":"巴塞上禮拜六喺國家打吡作客贏皇馬3:0，美斯喺呢場大戰入一粒兼有一次助攻，梗係猛啦。不過最誇張嘅係，原來美斯成場波幾乎冇跑過，一直行行企企！西班牙《馬卡報》根據統計報道，話喺國家打吡踢足嘅美斯，超過八成時間係喺度行緊，足足有83.1%時間。其餘時間，美斯有10.8%係慢跑緊，真正跑緊嘅時間係4.95%，另外1.15%就係全速跑，即係大約得一分鐘左右咋！企喺度都搞掂皇馬，球王係得嘅！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://90l.tribuna.com/images/c2/a9/f8/c2a9f899ae7d4c7cb9eddefec70e2a9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F90l.tribuna.com%2Fimages%2Fc2%2Fa9%2Ff8%2Fc2a9f899ae7d4c7cb9eddefec70e2a9b.jpg&h=66f3eb41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4db7fc7d58900fcc9a3c8fe5f4554a2f02e6467d","tid":511041,"uid":16061,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:44:39.000Z","msg":"咁唔係代表隊友都好強咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24571979b4e692792a6d5854db1eb64d94e24ac2","tid":511041,"uid":1977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:45:37.000Z","msg":"美斯企係度都要搵兩個mark佢啦<br />\n所以佢唔郁可能仲好"},{"pid":"c8b519faa19b35283a96fc8e52f526a407501682","tid":511041,"uid":115323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:46:40.000Z","msg":"美欺都係人 都想行行企企又一day"},{"pid":"1326376a3291c038225510a8befda0d52dd55503","tid":511041,"uid":55981,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"24571979b4e692792a6d5854db1eb64d94e24ac2","tid":511041,"uid":1977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:45:37.000Z","msg":"美斯企係度都要搵兩個mark佢啦<br />\n所以佢唔郁可能仲好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T05:48:04.000Z","msg":"高華錫寧願睇實佢都唔跑返去追個快攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a45c96a20b2110d540acf18597c8e11da0aa780","tid":511041,"uid":85819,"like":7,"disli